OOC Radio for FH6
=================

This project is a derivative work licensed under the GNU General Public
License v3.0 (see LICENSE). It is a stripped-down fork, single-purpose
mod: it plays only the "Out of Character Radio" stream and has no web
dashboard.

Attribution chain:

  - Forked from "FH6 Universal Radio" by g0ldyy
    (https://github.com/g0ldyy/fh6-universal-radio), GPLv3.
    Thanks also to @odexine (https://github.com/de-odex) for that
    project's Local Files playback work, carried in via the shared
    proxy/FMOD/DX12 plumbing this fork retains.

  - fh6-universal-radio was itself inspired by "Big John"'s
    closed-source FH6 Spotify radio mod (an unrelated, separately
    licensed project -- no code or implementation details from that
    mod are included here).

What changed in this fork: removed the local files/Spotify/YouTube
Music/Jellyfin/external-audio/vanilla-passthrough sources, removed the
HTTP dashboard and bundled web UI entirely, and added a single
hardcoded "OOC Radio" source that streams radio.oocradio.com and polls
api.oocradio.com/v1 for now-playing/live-presenter metadata shown
in-game.
